<p>Armie posted a photo of him and Elizabeth in happier times, and wrote: 'Thirteen years as best friends, soulmates, partners and then parents. It has been an incredible journey, but together, we've decided to turn the page and move on from our marriage.</p>

<p>'As we enter into this next chapter, our children and relationship as co-parents and dear friends will remain our priority.</p>

<p>'We understand this news lends itself to public dialogue, but in the interest of our children and our family, we're asking for privacy, compassion and love during this time.'</p>

<p>Armie and Elizabeth wed in 2010, and welcomed daughter Harper, five, and son Ford, three.</p>

